Overview:


This will provide you with all Feautures to protect you and your children from Torrents,Viruses and any other  type of innapropriate content.





Protection:


This will flag any sort of innapropriate sites or videos; under the masters controll.
This also comes with a firewall to protect you from most viruses thi firewall has adjustable settings to Mach your life style.
It also comes with a mobile application for any type of smartphone this Feautures let's you know what your children are watching and also gives you primary controll of the computer eg shutdown scan for viruses and close program's.





Symbol:

The symbol will relate to a safe with a world inside it.
The world stands for the Internet when the world comes out of the safe it means it is unprotected.
If you see the safe starting to unlock that means that someone is currently hacking into your computer.
